  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要为GradeSync教育应用设计一个架构图，核心是两个入口：注册和登录。我想把起点放在Education_GradeSync这个主模块上。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Education_GradeSync",
        "Registrarse",
        "Iniciar Sesión"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白了，所以Inicio_del_App作为顶层容器，里面放主模块。那注册流程是不是要单独抽成一个子图？我看到需要收集学生完整信息。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Inicio_del_App",
        "Education_ClassroomService",
        "Registro"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，Registro子图要包含所有必填字段：Nome_Completo、Nome_de_Usuario、Data_de_Nascimento这些基本信息，还有Género、Email、Número_de_Telefone和Senha。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Nome_Completo",
        "Nome_de_Usuario",
        "Data_de_Nascimento",
        "Género",
        "Email",
        "Número_de_Telefone",
        "Senha"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好，我在Registro子图里把这些字段都加上了。Nome_Completo、Nome_de_Usuario和Data_de_Nascimento都指向Education_StudentDB，Número_de_Telefone指向Education_ClassroomService，这样对吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Education_StudentDB",
        "Education_ClassroomService"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对的，学生核心档案存在StudentDB，但手机号验证走ClassroomService。登录流程相对简单，放在Login子图里。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Login",
        "Usuario_Email",
        "Senha"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "登录只需要Usuario_Email和Senha两项？Usuario_Email是指用户名或邮箱都可以登录吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Usuario_Email",
        "Senha",
        "Education_ClassroomService"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "是的，支持用户名或邮箱二选一登录。Usuario_Email这个字段要关联到Education_ClassroomService做身份校验。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Usuario_Email",
        "Education_ClassroomService"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "已更新，Login子图里Usuario_Email指向Education_ClassroomService，Senha单独列出。我注意到主模块Education_GradeSync有两个分支，一个去注册B节点，一个去登录C节点，但C节点也叫Education_GradeSync？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Education_GradeSync",
        "Education_ClassroomService",
        "Education_GradeSync"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 9,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "repair",
      "utterance": "啊，这里有问题。Iniciar Sesión的终点应该是登录验证服务，不是Education_GradeSync本身。让我确认一下——应该是Education_ClassroomService负责登录鉴权，不是GradeSync。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Iniciar Sesión",
        "Education_ClassroomService"
      ],
      "is_repair": true
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 10,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "收到，所以Iniciar Sesión指向C节点，C节点代表登录服务，关联到Education_ClassroomService。那Registrarse指向的B节点是Education_ClassroomService，负责注册流程，这样结构就一致了。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Registrarse",
        "Education_ClassroomService",
        "Iniciar Sesión"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 11,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "等等，我需要再理清楚：注册流程B节点是Education_ClassroomService，但里面Nome_Completo、Nome_de_Usuario、Data_de_Nascimento都是存到Education_StudentDB，只有Número_de_Telefone是ClassroomService。这个混合存储的逻辑要在图上体现清楚。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Education_ClassroomService",
        "Education_StudentDB",
        "Nome_Completo",
        "Nome_de_Usuario",
        "Data_de_Nascimento",
        "Número_de_Telefone"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 12,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "明白了，我用不同目标标注来区分：Nome_Completo[Education_StudentDB]、Nome_de_Usuario[Education_StudentDB]、Data_de_Nascimento[Education_StudentDB]，而Número_de_Telefone[Education_ClassroomService]。Género、Email、Senha暂时不标注存储位置。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Género",
        "Email",
        "Senha"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 13,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "Género和Email也应该存到StudentDB，Senha需要单独处理做加密存储。不过当前版本可以先简化，Senha不标注具体服务。Login子图的Senha同理。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Senha",
        "StudentDB"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 14,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "好的，保持当前设计。三个子图结构确认：Inicio_del_App包含主入口和两条分支；Registro包含7个字段，其中3个明确指向StudentDB，1个指向ClassroomService；Login包含2个字段，Usuario_Email指向ClassroomService。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Inicio_del_App",
        "Registro",
        "Login"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 15,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "再检查一下命名一致性：Data_de_Nascimento和Número_de_Telefone用了下划线，但Género和Email没有，这个需要统一吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
